# Test-utils templates (from `test_utils.json`)

Summarizes **4** files under **`app/test-utils/`** (see [`.agents/file-lists/test_utils.json`](../file-lists/test_utils.json)). Shared helpers for **Vitest** and snapshot tests.

## Inventory snapshot

| Fact | Typical value |
| --- | --- |
| Files | `createSnapshotRootElm.ts`, `fixSnapshotHashClassName.ts`, `mockTypeGuardFnConfig.ts`, `replaceSnapshotMarkers.ts` |
| Extensions | `.ts` |

## Snapshot root (UI tests)

```typescript
import { fixSnapshotHashClassName } from "./fixSnapshotHashClassName";
import { replaceSnapshotMarkers } from "./replaceSnapshotMarkers";

export function createSnapshotRootElm(): HTMLElement {
  fixSnapshotHashClassName(document.body);
  replaceSnapshotMarkers();
  return document.body;
}
```

## Usage in tests

```typescript
import { render } from "@testing-library/react";
import { createSnapshotRootElm } from "test-utils/createSnapshotRootElm";
import { describe, expect, it } from "vitest";

describe("Foo", () => {
  it("renders", (): void => {
    render(<Foo />);
    expect(createSnapshotRootElm()).toMatchSnapshot();
  });
});
```

